%%{init: {"sequence": {"mirrorActors": false}}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    actor Manager
    participant UI as Reports Dashboard
    participant API as Analytics API
    participant Agg as Data Aggregator
    participant DB as Database

    Manager->>UI: Open Productivity Reports
    UI->>API: GET /api/reports/productivity?period=month

    API->>DB: Fetch tasks, time_entries, completions
    API->>Agg: Process raw data

    par Parallel Aggregation
        Agg->>Agg: Group by user
        Agg->>Agg: Calculate completion rate
        Agg->>Agg: Compute avg cycle time
        Agg->>Agg: Measure on-time delivery %
    end

    Agg->>Agg: Normalize scores across team
    Agg-->>API: Aggregated metrics

    API->>API: Remove subjective inputs (no manager ratings)
    API->>API: Weight only objective data
    API-->>UI: {users[], metrics[], rankings[]}
    UI-->>Manager: Display charts + rankings

    Manager->>UI: Click on team member
    UI->>API: GET /api/reports/user/{id}
    API->>DB: Fetch user task history (90 days)
    API->>Agg: Calculate trends
    Agg-->>API: {completionTrend, velocityTrend, qualityScore}
    API-->>UI: Performance card with trends

    Manager->>UI: Export report
    UI->>API: GET /api/reports/export?format=pdf
    API->>Agg: Generate report document
    Agg-->>API: PDF buffer
    API-->>UI: Download: performance_review_feb2026.pdf
